527
00:35:31,370 --> 00:35:34,330
If there's a problem, we'll just figure it out together.

528
00:35:34,330 --> 00:35:36,330
Learn from it and don't make the same mistake again.

529
00:35:36,330 --> 00:35:41,030
Lu Jiming, you helped me out with Qinhe.

530
00:35:41,030 --> 00:35:44,370
So I'm supposed to sit here and listen to your lecture?

531
00:35:44,370 --> 00:35:46,810
I haven't asked you yet.

532
00:35:46,810 --> 00:35:48,762
Tell me honestly.

533
00:35:48,762 --> 00:35:51,590
Where did you get the money to buy stocks?

534
00:35:51,590 --> 00:35:53,400
It's from...

535
00:35:54,660 --> 00:35:56,856
I had my ways.

536
00:35:56,856 --> 00:35:58,858
Is the money clean?

537
00:35:58,858 --> 00:36:01,130
How could you possibly get so much money?

538
00:36:01,130 --> 00:36:04,760
