543
00:36:20,330 --> 00:36:22,450
- No, Dad.
- I'm warning you.

544
00:36:24,850 --> 00:36:27,318
Don't overestimate yourself.

545
00:36:27,318 --> 00:36:30,180
Don't simply touch the money that shouldn't be touched.

546
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:32,320
Do you hear me?

547
00:36:33,488 --> 00:36:36,660
Come on. You just won't listen to whatever I have to say. Is that it?

548
00:36:36,660 --> 00:36:38,680
I was going to...

549
00:36:40,160 --> 00:36:42,560
Forget it. Why did I fret about you?

550
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:45,314
Did I ask you to?

551
00:36:45,314 --> 00:36:47,930
So long as you don't make trouble for me.

552
00:36:49,130 --> 00:36:50,700
Eat your food with the soup.

553
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:52,560
And leave when you're finished.

554
00:36:56,050 --> 00:36:58,050
You two...

555
00:36:58,050 --> 00:36:59,870
What is the matter with you two?

556
00:36:59,870 --> 00:37:01,390
Why can't you just get along?

557
00:37:01,390 --> 00:37:03,330
Weren't you two talking?

558
00:37:03,330 --> 00:37:05,670
Why did you butt heads again?

559
00:37:06,370 --> 00:37:09,660
To be frank, your dad feels bad for troubling you.

560
00:37:09,660 --> 00:37:13,668
He hasn't been eating and sleeping well these days.

561
00:37:13,668 --> 00:37:15,280
So don't argue with him.

562
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:17,470
No, Madam Liu. I want to persuade him.

563
00:37:17,470 --> 00:37:20,610
But what's the point? Would he listen?

564
00:37:20,610 --> 00:37:23,860
His ego is too big and he can't let it go.

565
00:37:23,860 --> 00:37:27,330
Your father just doesn't want to implicate you.

566
00:37:27,330 --> 00:37:29,980
He doesn't want you to spend any more money.

567
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:31,370
Don't worry, Madam Liu.

568
00:37:31,370 --> 00:37:34,150
I'll figure out what to do about the money.

569
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:38,800
Then, go and get your dad to come to eat.

570
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:41,100
He hasn't eaten yet.

571
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:42,590
Okay.

572
00:38:14,950 --> 00:38:17,790
Hey. Once you get the bonus from the project,

573
00:38:17,790 --> 00:38:19,440
you should listen to me and buy a car.

574
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:22,800
Taking the subway to get to and from work is too tiring.

575
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:25,468
It's fine. I'm used to it.

576
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:27,912
I almost forgot.

577
00:38:27,912 --> 00:38:30,600
Your boyfriend can be your chauffeur.

578
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:33,500
No wonder you don't need a car. It's all good.

579
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:35,290
Sorry, excuse me.

580
00:38:35,290 --> 00:38:38,834
How do I use WeChat Pay?

581
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:44,208
Click open and then pay.

582
00:38:44,208 --> 00:38:45,121
Yes, click that.

583
00:38:45,121 --> 00:38:47,850
Receive payment. There you go.

584
00:38:47,850 --> 00:38:49,700
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

585
00:38:49,730 --> 00:38:51,140
I just returned from overseas.

586
00:38:51,140 --> 00:38:53,936
