587
00:39:00,230 --> 00:39:02,130
Senior?

588
00:39:02,130 --> 00:39:06,006
Ning Meng? You're Ning Meng, right?

589
00:39:06,006 --> 00:39:09,310
Yes, I am. Long time no see.

590
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:12,220
