618
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:43,700
Ning Meng, Weiran went through a lot overseas.

619
00:40:43,700 --> 00:40:45,370
It was tough on him.

620
00:40:45,370 --> 00:40:47,838
As for me,

621
00:40:47,838 --> 00:40:51,030
