00:41:09,770 --> 00:41:10,810
It's nothing.

628
00:41:10,810 --> 00:41:13,770
I just want to give you a gentle reminder.

629
00:41:13,770 --> 00:41:16,220
If he gets angry in the future,

630
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:17,980
