632
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,260
Don't fight with him.

633
00:41:21,260 --> 00:41:24,516
When he calms down, you can talk it through then.

634
00:41:26,630 --> 00:41:30,390
This is because of me.

635
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:34,604
It's my fault.

636
00:41:41,290 --> 00:41:43,640
Oh, I'm sorry.

637
00:41:43,640 --> 00:41:47,380
My ride is here. I have to go.

638
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:49,940
If you need anything, you can contact me through WeChat.

639
00:41:49,940 --> 00:41:51,220
Sure, I will.

640
00:41:51,220 --> 00:41:53,180
Wishing you two happiness.

